{
  "episode_id": "2026-07-23",
  "chunks": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "听众朋友大家好，欢迎收听AI每日先锋，今天是2026年7月23日。我是苏晴。",
      "start": 1.0,
      "duration": 8.925,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_001_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_001_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "大家好，我是周航。苏晴，你今天刷到百度文心的那个新闻没有？",
      "start": 10.374,
      "duration": 4.746,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_002_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_002_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我跟你说，刷到了刷到了！文心助手那个任务Agent，把Claude和GPT系列全干趴下了，拿了国际权威智能体评测的全球第一。 我第一反应是——真的假的？然后我点进去一看，榜单还挺硬核的，不是那种野榜。",
      "start": 15.617,
      "duration": 17.87,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_003_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_003_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你注意啊，这个榜单考的不是你会不会聊天，而是真刀真枪看你的Agent能不能干活——任务规划、工具调用、多步推理，这三板斧全砍下来，文心拿了第一，含金量挺高。",
      "start": 33.94,
      "duration": 13.603,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_004_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_004_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这也太提气了吧！以前咱们聊大模型，张嘴就是GPT几几几、Claude几几几，国产的往往是用\"也非常优秀\"、\"达到国际先进水平\"这种委婉措辞。这次不一样，直接登顶，而且是被国际权威机构认可的。",
      "start": 47.948,
      "duration": 24.879,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_005_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_005_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "但说白了，登顶这件事本身还不是最重要的，最重要的是它背后传递的信号。中国的大模型开始从\"能对话\"跨越到\"能办事\"了。以前你问它问题，它给你一段漂亮话；现在你让它干活，它真能把活儿给你干完。",
      "start": 73.26,
      "duration": 18.784,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_006_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_006_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我大概理解了，这个Agent就相当于一个会思考的小秘书？你告诉它\"帮我订明天去上海的机票，要靠窗的，下午到\"，它自己拆解任务、调API、查航班、比价格，最后把结果给你。",
      "start": 92.509,
      "duration": 21.483,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_007_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_007_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你这个类比还挺准的。 技术层面，它要听懂你的意图，拆成子任务，调用不同工具，处理中间可能出现的异常。比如查航班时遇到延误，它得知道换个方案；付款时遇到余额不足，它得知道提示你。这一整条链路能跑通，才叫真正的Agent能力。",
      "start": 114.454,
      "duration": 19.306,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_008_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_008_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "那对咱们普通人有啥影响？是不是以后用百度系产品，文心助手就能帮我把琐事全包了？",
      "start": 134.211,
      "duration": 6.966,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_009_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_009_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "短期内还没那么神，但方向是对的。百度这次把Agent能力做扎实了，等于在AI应用层拿到了一个制高点。以后各家拼的不再是\"我的模型参数多少亿\"，而是\"我的Agent能在多少真实场景里把事办成\"。",
      "start": 141.677,
      "duration": 16.912,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_010_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_010_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哈，这话让我想起今天金句的那句话——从追赶到领跑，中国AI正从\"刷榜单\"走向\"深落地\"。技术狂飙之后，价值兑现才是真战场。",
      "start": 159.027,
      "duration": 15.369,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_011_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_011_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "对，\"深落地\"其实是整个行业的转向。光在benchmark上刷分刷到全球第一没用，最终还是得看你能不能解决真实问题。",
      "start": 174.857,
      "duration": 9.404,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_012_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_012_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "说到\"深落地\"，我特别想跟你聊聊医疗AI。这个赛道卷了十年了，我记得2016年那会儿就有人喊\"AI看片比医生准\"、\"AI要替代放射科医生\"，结果呢？",
      "start": 184.706,
      "duration": 14.89,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_013_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_013_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "结果牛皮吹得震天响，落地嘛……说实话，磕磕绊绊。医疗是个高度保守的行业，容错率极低。AI判断错了，医生不敢用；医生自己看，又用不上AI。两边拉扯了十年。",
      "start": 200.07,
      "duration": 14.169,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_014_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_014_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "所以这次大纲里说\"终于悟了\"，我觉得这词用得特别形象。那到底悟出了啥？",
      "start": 214.666,
      "duration": 5.834,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_015_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_015_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你注意啊，最大的认知转变是：不再死磕\"替代医生\"了。十年下来大家都想明白了，AI短期内干不了医生这活儿。医生的临床判断、医患沟通、伦理决策，这些东西不是几个模型能搞定的。",
      "start": 220.964,
      "duration": 14.125,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_016_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_016_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "那现在走的是什么路子？",
      "start": 235.506,
      "duration": 2.133,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_017_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_017_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "现在是\"给医院装buff\"——AI变成医院的基础设施，跟CT机、核磁共振一个层级，是底层能力底座，不是前台医生。",
      "start": 238.075,
      "duration": 8.969,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_018_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_018_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哦我懂了，有点像游戏里给英雄装备。医生是英雄，AI是装备，装备越强英雄越能打。",
      "start": 247.461,
      "duration": 9.143,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_019_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_019_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你这个类比相当贴切。具体落地比如AI辅助诊断、AI影像分析、AI病历生成、AI用药审核——这些都是嵌进医院工作流里的工具，医生用着顺手，效率提高，错误率下降。",
      "start": 257.1,
      "duration": 15.693,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_020_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_020_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我跟你说，这个转变对行业意义特别大。商业逻辑整个变了——以前想To C，让患者自己用AI看病，那付费意愿很弱；现在To B，直接卖给医院，付费方明确，预算稳定，账也好算。",
      "start": 273.205,
      "duration": 22.049,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_021_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_021_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "而且医院一旦用起来，数据飞轮就转起来了。AI用得越多，积累的临床数据越多，模型迭代越快，越用越好用，别的医院一看，也想用。这不就是强者愈强嘛。",
      "start": 295.733,
      "duration": 13.168,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_022_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_022_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "那以后我们去挂号、看医生，是不是能明显感觉到AI的存在？",
      "start": 309.333,
      "duration": 4.702,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_023_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_023_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "会的。比如你进去看病，医生面前那个系统可能已经把你过去三年的体检报告、用药记录、家族病史全整理好了，还自动提示了几个需要重点关注的风险点。医生不再是\"打字机\"，而是真正的决策者。",
      "start": 314.503,
      "duration": 17.304,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_024_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_024_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这画面感一下就来了。说白了，AI把医生从繁琐的文书工作里解放出来，让医生把时间花在\"看病\"本身上。",
      "start": 332.297,
      "duration": 12.147,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_025_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_025_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你这话说到点子上了。十年悟道，悟出的就是这个——AI不是来抢饭碗的，是来让专业的人干更专业的事的。",
      "start": 344.921,
      "duration": 8.882,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_026_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_026_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对了，说到AIGC生态，最近美图干了件挺狠的事——砸了一个亿悬赏AI影像的Builder。",
      "start": 354.221,
      "duration": 8.882,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_027_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_027_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "一个亿？真的假的？",
      "start": 363.542,
      "duration": 1.611,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_028_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_028_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "真的，我专门查了。美图启动了一个产品挑战赛，奖金池一个亿，面向全行业征集AI影像应用开发者。",
      "start": 365.565,
      "duration": 10.144,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_029_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_029_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你注意啊，美图这步棋很聪明。它自己虽然有美图秀秀这种国民级应用，但AIGC时代，光靠一个App打天下已经远远不够了。它需要生态。",
      "start": 376.202,
      "duration": 10.991,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_030_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_030_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "所以这相当于美图出钱、出流量、出平台，让开发者来基于它的底层能力搭应用？",
      "start": 387.602,
      "duration": 9.099,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_031_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_031_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "对，本质上就是在建AIGC时代的\"App Store\"。你做出来好用的AI修图、AI视频、AI生图工具，挂在我美图生态里，我帮你分发，大家一起赚钱。",
      "start": 397.188,
      "duration": 14.125,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_032_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_032_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这个思路其实跟苹果当年搞App Store一个逻辑。早期靠硬件赚钱，成熟期靠生态赚钱。美图现在明显是奔着生态去了。",
      "start": 411.755,
      "duration": 12.166,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_033_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_033_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "而且一个亿对美图来说不算伤筋动骨，但足以吸引一大批中小开发者。高手在民间嘛，说不定就冒出来一个现象级的AI影像应用。",
      "start": 424.381,
      "duration": 11.363,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_034_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_034_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哈，那以后我们手机上可能就会出现一堆基于美图底层能力的AI小工具了。",
      "start": 436.215,
      "duration": 7.924,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_035_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_035_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "说到办公工具这块，最近金山办公也挺有意思。田然提了AI办公助理的三个标准——\"懂你、能交付、专业操作\"。",
      "start": 444.551,
      "duration": 10.623,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_036_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_036_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我跟你说，这三个标准其实挺狠的，等于把市面上那些\"智障办公助手\"全给比下去了。",
      "start": 455.619,
      "duration": 10.362,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_037_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_037_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你展开讲讲。",
      "start": 466.436,
      "duration": 1.611,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_038_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_038_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
