    {
      "id": 39,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "\"懂你\"是基础中的基础，你得知道我是谁、我在干啥、我的习惯是什么。一个不记得我昨天做啥的助手，那就是个假助手。",
      "start": 468.487,
      "duration": 11.252,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_039_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_039_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "\"能交付\"这点更重要。现在很多AI办公产品，你让它写个报告，它给你大纲；你让它做个表，它给你思路。最后落地还是得你自己搞。",
      "start": 480.217,
      "duration": 10.512,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_040_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_040_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对，交付就是它得真把活儿干完。一个能直接给你的成品，不是一份需要你加工的半成品。",
      "start": 491.21,
      "duration": 8.664,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_041_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_041_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "\"专业操作\"是天花板。你注意啊，办公不是聊天，专业操作意味着它得能调用企业内部系统、操作各种专业软件，不是表面上的花拳绣腿。",
      "start": 500.3,
      "duration": 11.842,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_042_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_042_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这三个标准其实是递进的：懂你是前提，能交付是门槛，专业操作是分水岭。能同时做到这三点的产品，才能真正杀进企业核心工作流。",
      "start": 512.612,
      "duration": 14.933,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_043_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_043_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "WPS现在要是能把这三点都打透，那对微软Office的冲击会非常大。尤其在国内市场，性价比加上AI能力的组合，挺能打的。",
      "start": 528.006,
      "duration": 10.144,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_044_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_044_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "那说到行业风向标，前几天WAIC 2026开幕了吧？十大趋势你看了没？",
      "start": 538.606,
      "duration": 9.578,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_045_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_045_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "看了，每年这个时候各家都把自己的压箱底拿出来。我跟你说我印象最深的几条。",
      "start": 548.65,
      "duration": 6.879,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_046_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_046_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我先来一个，具身智能肯定是大热门吧？",
      "start": 555.962,
      "duration": 5.529,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_047_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_047_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "必须的。具身智能这两年从概念到落地，进展比大家想象得快。我看到好几个展台，机器人已经能完成一些复杂的工厂任务了，动作丝滑度比去年明显上了一个台阶。",
      "start": 561.898,
      "duration": 13.758,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_048_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_048_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "大模型这块呢？",
      "start": 576.126,
      "duration": 1.48,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_049_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_049_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "大模型本身已经不是新闻了，今年大家聊的是多模态原生——文字、图像、视频、音频，从底层架构就是一个模态，不是我先生成文本再翻译成图片。这种原生多模态能力，是下一代模型的标配。",
      "start": 578.007,
      "duration": 16.955,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_050_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_050_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我比较关注AI治理这一块。",
      "start": 595.373,
      "duration": 4.876,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_051_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_051_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 52,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这个话题越来越重要了。技术跑得快，规则跟不上，监管就容易出问题。今年WAIC上能看到很多关于AI伦理、版权、隐私的国际讨论，各国监管思路差别也挺大。",
      "start": 600.741,
      "duration": 14.604,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_052_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_052_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "还有啥趋势值得聊的？",
      "start": 615.796,
      "duration": 3.396,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_053_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_053_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 54,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "还有Agent生态、AI for Science、AI普惠教育等等。说白了，十大趋势背后就是一个主线——AI从极客玩具变成社会基础设施，渗透到各行各业里去。",
      "start": 619.682,
      "duration": 13.864,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_054_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_054_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 55,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这个主线跟我前面说的\"深落地\"是一回事。",
      "start": 634.046,
      "duration": 5.312,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_055_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_055_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 56,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "对，技术狂飙之后，价值兑现才是真战场。这句话咱们今天反复用，因为它是真的。",
      "start": 639.843,
      "duration": 6.008,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_056_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_056_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 57,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "那我最后给你做个收尾吧——今天咱们聊了三件事：百度文心任务Agent登顶全球，标志中国AI从\"能对话\"到\"能办事\"；医疗AI十年悟道，从想\"替代医生\"转向\"给医院装buff\"；还有美图一个亿砸生态、金山办公定标准、WAIC十大趋势指向落地。",
      "start": 646.331,
      "duration": 26.335,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_057_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_057_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 58,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这三件事看似散，其实都指向同一个底层逻辑：中国AI正在穿越\"技术神话\"的阶段，进入\"产业兑现\"的阶段。能不能把技术变成实实在在的价值，决定了下一轮谁笑到最后。",
      "start": 673.066,
      "duration": 14.212,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_058_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_058_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 59,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "听众朋友，今天的AI每日先锋就到这里，咱们明天见。",
      "start": 687.756,
      "duration": 5.007,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_059_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_059_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 60,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "明天见。",
      "start": 693.226,
      "duration": 1.045,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_060_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_060_lively.mp3"
